{"about_the_game":"<strong>Play with Friends PVP PVE &amp; Co-Op!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2504540/extras/playeramount.gif?t=1707830597\" /><br><br>Unleash Your Strategic Prowess in a Multidimensional Battle Arena. Prepare for a thrilling and unpredictable journey into the world of Cube Royale, where strategy, cunning, and the element of surprise reign supreme. Engage in fierce multiplayer showdowns with up to 6 players in this turn-based, battle royale-style game.<br><br><br><br><strong>Collect Protect Attack &amp; Trap!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2504540/extras/collect_protect_attack_trap.gif?t=1707830597\" /><br><br>Be a hunter, collector, defender, and aggressor all at once! Every move you make opens up chances to score points, defeat rivals, set traps, or trigger chain reactions. Stay alive and gather the most points to win the match!<br><br><br><br><strong>Use your Power-ups!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2504540/extras/powerups.gif?t=1707830597\" /><br><br>Power-ups give you advantages over your foes. Evaluate your options with every move. Use them strategically against your opponents and sweep them off the board.<br><br><br><br><strong>Waves can destroy you!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2504540/extras/waves.gif?t=1707830597\" /><br><br>Keep an eye out for the formidable waves that can potentially wipe out your CUBES. Yet, if used wisely, they can become a game-changing factor, bringing you one step closer to victory!<br><br><br><br><strong>Accentuate your gameplay with more style!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2504540/extras/skins.gif?t=1707830597\" />